{"TopicId":88012,"ForumId":20,"TopicTitle":"Looking for a HUD Mod","CreatedByName":"cnumartyr","CreatedById":126598,"CreatedDateTime":"2014-10-20T16:48:01Z","PageNum":1,"Articles":[{"CreatedByName":"cnumartyr","CreatedById":126598,"CreatedDateTime":"2014-10-20T16:48:01Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003EHey guys.\u003C/p\u003E\u003Cp\u003ESo I\u0027m looking for a mod to supplement the NavBall. What I\u0027d like is a digital readout of my pitch, heading, and rotation that I can move around. Something like what you get on some IVAs with RPM but on the HUD outside the ship.\u003C/p\u003E\u003Cp\u003EThanks!\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Malah","CreatedById":96644,"CreatedDateTime":"2014-10-20T18:13:33Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003EHello, I don\u0027t know if you have seen something like \u003Ca href=\u0022https://forum.kerbalspaceprogram.com/threads/40730\u0022 rel=\u0022external nofollow\u0022\u003ESteamGauges\u003C/a\u003E or \u003Ca href=\u0022https://forum.kerbalspaceprogram.com/threads/81543\u0022 rel=\u0022external nofollow\u0022\u003ENavHud\u003C/a\u003E others interesting hud you can have:\u003C/p\u003E\u003Cp\u003E- \u003Ca href=\u0022https://forum.kerbalspaceprogram.com/threads/80277\u0022 rel=\u0022external nofollow\u0022\u003EKerbal Flight Indicators draws a couple of markers directly in your field of view (a minimalistic NavHud)\u003C/a\u003E\u003C/p\u003E\u003Cp\u003E- \u003Ca href=\u0022https://forum.kerbalspaceprogram.com/threads/85353\u0022 rel=\u0022external nofollow\u0022\u003ENavUtilities to help the landing with a shuttle or a plane\u003C/a\u003E\u003C/p\u003E\u003Cp\u003E- \u003Ca href=\u0022https://forum.kerbalspaceprogram.com/threads/43901\u0022 rel=\u0022external nofollow\u0022\u003EDocking Port Alignment Indicator to help the docking, but I dont know if that work again with KSP 0.25\u003C/a\u003E\u003C/p\u003E\u003Cp\u003EIf you search more information on the hud, you can look on \u003Ca href=\u0022https://forum.kerbalspaceprogram.com/threads/54533\u0022 rel=\u0022external nofollow\u0022\u003EVOID\u003C/a\u003E, \u003Ca href=\u0022http://kerbal.curseforge.com/ksp-mods/220529-kdata\u0022 rel=\u0022external nofollow\u0022\u003Ekdata\u003C/a\u003E, \u003Ca href=\u0022https://forum.kerbalspaceprogram.com/threads/80842\u0022 rel=\u0022external nofollow\u0022\u003EKerbal Flight Data\u003C/a\u003E or a more generic and powerful \u003Ca href=\u0022https://forum.kerbalspaceprogram.com/threads/18230\u0022 rel=\u0022external nofollow\u0022\u003EKerbal Engineer Redux\u003C/a\u003E or \u003Ca href=\u0022https://forum.kerbalspaceprogram.com/threads/12384\u0022 rel=\u0022external nofollow\u0022\u003EMechJeb\u003C/a\u003E ...\u003C/p\u003E\u003Cp\u003EEDIT: I\u0027ve forgot 2 others mods which can be what you search: \u003Ca href=\u0022https://forum.kerbalspaceprogram.com/threads/40730\u0022 rel=\u0022external nofollow\u0022\u003ESteamGauges\u003C/a\u003E and \u003Ca href=\u0022https://forum.kerbalspaceprogram.com/threads/80277\u0022 rel=\u0022external nofollow\u0022\u003EKerbal Flight Indicators\u003C/a\u003E\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cspan class=\u0022ipsType_reset ipsType_medium ipsType_light\u0022 data-excludequote=\u0022\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cstrong\u003EEdited \u003Ctime datetime=\u00222014-10-20T23:49:43Z\u0022 title=\u002210/20/2014 11:49  PM\u0022 data-short=\u00229 yr\u0022\u003EOctober 20, 2014\u003C/time\u003E by Malah\u003C/strong\u003E\n\u003Cbr\u003Eadd 2 others mods\n\u003C/span\u003E\n"}]}